[metadata]
Name:Memoricide — NameCard choose-name exile from gy/hand/library
Goal:Win
Turns:5
Difficulty:Medium
Description:P0 casts Memoricide targeting P1 who holds 2 copies of Lightning Bolt in hand, 1 in graveyard, and 1 in library. The NameCard effect should allow P0 to name "Lightning Bolt" and then exile all copies from P1's graveyard, hand, and library (DBExile, ChangeType$ Card.NamedCard, Hidden$ True). If NameCard is a no-op the copies survive. Regression for 2010 WC tracker mtg-914 B4.

